title: Create Memories with your Family! Res Lease in Round Rock. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Come and see this incredible 2-stories with 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom home in Round Rock, TX!', 'With an excellent location in Round Rock west area with great schools near!', 'You will love everything this house has to offer, welcoming you to the 1st floor with its 2 living spaces and the fully equipped open kitchen, with ready to use appliances: microwave, gas range, dishwasher and a fridge; plenty of counterspace and wood cabinetry to utilize, plus access to the backyard.', 'The 2nd floor has a spacious family room and 3 bedrooms, all with laminated wood flooring.', 'The main bedroom has a closet and an ample full bathroom with dual vanity, walk-in shower and an amazing garden tub.', 'Additional amenities are a 2-car attached garage, laundry room and a huge private fenced backyard to enjoy the evenings with your loved ones or just relax.', 'Tour the home today, it will lease fast!!', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 2744031)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
